trans-unit.source: Contains filter criteria for data extracted from a workflow instance in a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 에 워크플로 인스턴스에서 추출 된 데이터에 대 한 필터 조건을 포함 한 <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A TrackingDataItemValue specifies the value of a piece of data extracted from a workflow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]TrackingDataItemValue는 워크플로에서 추출할 데이터의 값을 지정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: It is used to constrain the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> in a query of the tracking data base used by a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>에 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> 에서 사용 하는 기본 추적 데이터의 쿼리에</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 의해 반환 된 개체의</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> 집합을 제한 하는 데 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: You can add TrackingDataItemValue objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to specify that the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> be constrained to those possessing the specified set of extracted data.
trans-unit.target: TrackingDataItemValue 개체를 추가할 수 있습니다 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>되도록 지정 하려면 집합이 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>에서 반환 된 개체 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>추출 된 데이터의 지정된 된 집합을 소유 하는 것을 제한할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> to a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: 기본 생성자는 초기화 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>를 null 참조 (`Nothing` Visual basic에서).</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must set all of these properties in order to configure the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue> 를 구성 하려면 이러한 모든 속성을 설정 해야

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"></xref> class by using the specified qualified name of an activity, data field name, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> representation of a data value.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> 데이터 필드 이름, 활동의 정규화 된 지정 된 이름을 사용 하 여 클래스 및 <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> 데이터 값의 표현입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> properties are set according to the values specified by the equivalent parameters to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>속성은 생성자에 대 한 동등한 매개 변수가 지정 된 값에 따라 설정 됩니다.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>

trans-unit.source: FieldName can, therefore, be set to specify an activity field or property; a member of an activity field or property; or a single element of an activity field or property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: FieldName 활동 필드나 속성을 지정 하려면 따라서 설정할 수 있습니다, 활동 필드나 속성의 구성원 구현 하는 활동 필드나 또는 속성 (또는 그룹의 멤버)의 단일 요소는 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>인터페이스.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>
